<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">Hi <%= @user.name.presence || "there" %>,</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">Welcome to Loop AI! You're all set to start collecting real feedback through conversations instead of forms.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-weight: 600;">Get started in 3 steps:</p>

<ol style="margin: 0 0 16px; padding-left: 20px;">
  <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Create a loop</strong> — name it and add a few questions about what you want to learn.</li>
  <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Activate it</strong> — this turns on your AI voice agent so respondents can start talking.</li>
  <li><strong>Share the link</strong> — send it to your users and watch feedback and insights show up on your dashboard.</li>
</ol>

<%= render "mailer/button", text: "Go to your dashboard", url: dashboard_url %>

<p style="margin: 16px 0 0;">Questions? Just reply to this email — we're happy to help.</p>
